The codes concerning all of the experiments are provided in the documents Resnet19_cifar10, Resnet19_cifar100, VGG_cifar10, and VGG_cifar100 respectively. 
In addition, the corresponding documents/files are named with the characters in the manuscript.
The dataset CIFAR10/100 is public available online. The website is: https://www.cs.toronto.edu/~kriz/cifar.html.
The raw data of experimental results are provided in the document "Experimental results".
20210812imagenet_train.npy,20210812imagenet_val.npy,20210812imagenet_test.npy, demonstrate the dataset ImageNet100.
